===Noun===
'''ma''' (not generally used in the plural)

#(''colloquially and in direct address'') [[Mother]], [[mama]].

====Usage note====
*Often capitalized when used to refer to a specific person.
:''Hey, Ma, I'd like you to meet my friend Jamie.''

